  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Timescape Viewer设计一个ER图，核心是一个叫Timescape的实体，它代表整个查看器，包含一个title字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape",
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Timescape作为根实体，title是string类型。那它下面应该关联哪些子系统？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Timescape需要管理多个Origin，这是数据来源的抽象。Origin有个name字段。另外还需要ScopeLegend和ScopePlotter，这两个是可视化组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Origin",
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter",
        "name"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ScopeLegend和ScopePlotter看起来是图例和绘图器，它们有属性吗？还是纯行为组件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "目前这两个可以设为空，主要是占位。重点是Timescape到Origin是一对多，到ScopeLegend也是一对多，到ScopePlotter是多对多关系，一个查看器可以有多个plotter，一个plotter也可能被复用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape",
        "Origin",
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我标记为\"n*m\"表示多对多。还有一个Window实体，应该是时间窗口吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Timescape"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Window表示用户查看的时间范围，有begin和end两个Timestamp，还有一个live字段表示是否实时模式。Timescape到Window也是一对多。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "begin",
        "end",
        "live",
        "Timescape"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Window关联到Timescape。现在数据层面呢？Signal怎么定义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Signal是核心数据信号，有name、description和unit三个字段。Origin通过owns关系拥有多个Signal，这是弱关联的一对多。同时ScopePlotter通过shows关系显示多个Signal，也是多对多。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "name",
        "description",
        "unit",
        "Origin",
        "ScopePlotter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ScopePlotter到Signal是多对多，那Origin到Signal是识别关系还是非识别？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Origin",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用虚线表示弱关联，Origin ||..|{ Signal，意思是每个Origin拥有多个Signal。接下来是Run，表示一次运行会话，有title字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Run",
        "title",
        "Origin",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Run。Origin到Run的关系是consists of吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Run",
        "Origin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Origin ||..|{ Run，一个数据来源包含多次运行。然后Window通过shows关系关联到Run，表示这个窗口显示哪次运行的数据，是多对一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Run",
        "shows"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "明白了。那Track是什么？我看到后面有Block。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Track",
        "Block"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Track是Run下面的轨道，目前先放个dummy value占位。Run ||--|{ Track表示一次运行有多条轨道。Track又通过弱关联拥有多个Signal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Track",
        "Run",
        "Signal",
        "dummy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Track到Signal也是弱关联吗？和Origin owns Signal有什么区别？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Track",
        "Signal",
        "Origin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Origin owns是所有权，Track has是引用关系，都用弱关联但语义不同。最后是Block，存储实际的时间序列数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block",
        "Track",
        "Origin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Block有哪些字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Block有begin、end两个Date，还有timestamps数组和values二维数组。Track到Block是一对多，因为一条轨道可以有多个数据块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block",
        "begin",
        "end",
        "timestamps",
        "values",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Track ||--o{ Block。我检查一下：Window的live字段类型是LiveMode，不是boolean？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "live",
        "LiveMode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "对，应该是LiveMode类型，不是boolean。另外ScopeLegend和ScopePlotter的关联关系名我确认一下，一个是n，一个是n*m。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "live",
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter",
        "Timescape"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正live为LiveMode。整个结构确认了：Timescape作为根，向下管理Origin、ScopeLegend、ScopePlotter、Window，数据流通过Signal、Run、Track、Block层级组织，关系都标注清楚了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape",
        "Origin",
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter",
        "Window",
        "Signal",
        "Run",
        "Track",
        "Block"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
